{
  "video_id": "Q6VbZ6oo_LU",
  "title": "Why Siri Still Sucks",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 600.0,
      "end_time": 2980.0,
      "text": "Hey Siri, what time is Westworld on?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2980.0,
      "end_time": 4550.0,
      "text": "Here are matches for Westworld."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 4550.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Westworld, Westworld, Beyond Westworld,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7000.0,
      "end_time": 8250.0,
      "text": "Westworld on a Budget."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 8250.0,
      "end_time": 10879.0,
      "text": "Siri has been around for almost seven years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10880.0,
      "end_time": 12610.0,
      "text": "but it still kinda sucks."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 12610.0,
      "end_time": 14830.0,
      "text": "Google Assistant and Amazon's Alexa"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 14830.0,
      "end_time": 17580.0,
      "text": "keep getting updated with cool new features,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 17580.0,
      "end_time": 21110.0,
      "text": "but Siri feels outdated and stuck in 2013."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 21110.0,
      "end_time": 22840.0,
      "text": "Here's what went wrong with Siri"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 22840.0,
      "end_time": 26330.0,
      "text": "and what Apple can do to fix some of the problems right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 26330.0,
      "end_time": 29189.0,
      "text": "Siri felt revolutionary when it first came out"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29190.0,
      "end_time": 31740.0,
      "text": "in 2011 on the iPhone 4S."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 31740.0,
      "end_time": 34769.0,
      "text": "While it wasn't the first digital assistant ever created,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 34770.0,
      "end_time": 37810.0,
      "text": "it felt almost magical to be able to talk to your iPhone"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 37810.0,
      "end_time": 39200.0,
      "text": "and have it respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 39200.0,
      "end_time": 41530.0,
      "text": "But the magic didn't last very long."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 41530.0,
      "end_time": 42700.0,
      "text": "Within a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 42700.0,
      "end_time": 45650.0,
      "text": "Google had a similar answer called Google Now."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45650.0,
      "end_time": 48170.0,
      "text": "Google Now tapped into Google's vast knowledge"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 48170.0,
      "end_time": 51700.0,
      "text": "of the internet to get you exactly what you asked for."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 51700.0,
      "end_time": 53580.0,
      "text": "You could ask things like, \"How old is Tom Cruise,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 53580.0,
      "end_time": 56730.0,
      "text": "or, \"show me cute pictures of corgi puppies,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 56730.0,
      "end_time": 58320.0,
      "text": "and you'd get exactly that."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 58320.0,
      "end_time": 61600.0,
      "text": "Siri started to look pretty dumb by comparison"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 61600.0,
      "end_time": 62490.0,
      "text": "and it never caught up."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 62490.0,
      "end_time": 65150.0,
      "text": "Now we have three major digital assistants"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 65150.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66720.0,
      "text": "fighting for your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 66720.0,
      "end_time": 69660.0,
      "text": "There's Apple's Siri, Google's Assistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 69660.0,
      "end_time": 71259.0,
      "text": "and Amazon's Alexa."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 73510.0,
      "text": "And Apple could actually look to those rivals"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 73510.0,
      "end_time": 75950.0,
      "text": "for inspiration to fix Siri now."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 75950.0,
      "end_time": 77710.0,
      "text": "The biggest problem with Siri today"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 77710.0,
      "end_time": 79390.0,
      "text": "is that it doesn't integrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 79400.0,
      "end_time": 81370.0,
      "text": "with third-party services very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 81370.0,
      "end_time": 83410.0,
      "text": "There are a few categories it does work with,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 83410.0,
      "end_time": 85840.0,
      "text": "like messaging or ride-hailing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 85840.0,
      "end_time": 88880.0,
      "text": "but for the most part it's a closed-off ecosystem."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 88880.0,
      "end_time": 91670.0,
      "text": "This turns out to be Alexa's greatest strength."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 91670.0,
      "end_time": 93750.0,
      "text": "There are thousands of third-party skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 93750.0,
      "end_time": 95960.0,
      "text": "and apps that work with Alexa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 95960.0,
      "end_time": 98800.0,
      "text": "meaning it's a wide-open ecosystem"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 98800.0,
      "end_time": 99620.0,
      "text": "where anything's possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 99620.0,
      "end_time": 101360.0,
      "text": "You can check your bank balance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 101360.0,
      "end_time": 103210.0,
      "text": "you can order a coffee from Starbucks"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 103210.0,
      "end_time": 105399.0,
      "text": "and have it waiting for you when you arrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 105400.0,
      "end_time": 106600.0,
      "text": "and it works with a lot more"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 106600.0,
      "end_time": 109900.0,
      "text": "smart home appliances than Siri does."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 109100.0,
      "end_time": 111430.0,
      "text": "And it's the same story with Google's Assistant."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 111430.0,
      "end_time": 112730.0,
      "text": "Think of it like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 112730.0,
      "end_time": 114640.0,
      "text": "How terrible would your iPhone be"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 114640.0,
      "end_time": 116990.0,
      "text": "if you couldn't download any third-party apps"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 116990.0,
      "end_time": 118200.0,
      "text": "from the App Store?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 118200.0,
      "end_time": 120339.0,
      "text": "That's the state we're in with Siri today."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 120340.0,
      "end_time": 122140.0,
      "text": "Another huge problem with Siri"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 122140.0,
      "end_time": 125530.0,
      "text": "is that there's so many fragmented versions of the service."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 125530.0,
      "end_time": 127210.0,
      "text": "Siri on the HomePod is mostly"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 127210.0,
      "end_time": 129680.0,
      "text": "just to ask for songs from Apple Music."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 129680.0,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "It can't even do basic stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133320.0,
      "text": "like checking your calendar appointments."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 133320.0,
      "end_time": 136570.0,
      "text": "Siri on the iPhone is different than Siri on the Mac,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 136570.0,
      "end_time": 139700.0,
      "text": "and that's different than Siri on the Apple TV"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 139700.0,
      "end_time": 140380.0,
      "text": "and the Apple Watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 140380.0,
      "end_time": 143660.0,
      "text": "Apple has failed to give you one consistent version of Siri,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 143660.0,
      "end_time": 146230.0,
      "text": "no matter which Apple device you're using."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 146230.0,
      "end_time": 148869.0,
      "text": "If a digital assistant's going to be successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 148870.0,
      "end_time": 151570.0,
      "text": "it needs to be the same, no matter where you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 151570.0,
      "end_time": 154280.0,
      "text": "in the home, in the car, in the office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 154280.0,
      "end_time": 156480.0,
      "text": "and no matter what gadget you're using."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 156480.0,
      "end_time": 159600.0,
      "text": "This is another area Amazon's Alexa"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 159600.0,
      "end_time": 160760.0,
      "text": "and Google Assistant excel."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 160760.0,
      "end_time": 163600.0,
      "text": "Today, Siri is a fragmented mess"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 163600.0,
      "end_time": 165600.0,
      "text": "when it should be the same everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 167490.0,
      "text": "Apple should unify it so there's one version"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 167490.0,
      "end_time": 169540.0,
      "text": "across all of its devices."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 169540.0,
      "end_time": 172459.0,
      "text": "The final major problem with Siri is updates."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 172460.0,
      "end_time": 174300.0,
      "text": "While Google Assistant and Alexa"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 174300.0,
      "end_time": 176450.0,
      "text": "constantly get better over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 176450.0,
      "end_time": 178679.0,
      "text": "Siri only gets significant updates"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 178680.0,
      "end_time": 182360.0,
      "text": "once a year with new versions of iOS on the iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 182360.0,
      "end_time": 183810.0,
      "text": "Apple should really start looking at"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 183810.0,
      "end_time": 185910.0,
      "text": "Amazon and Google's strategy here"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 185910.0,
      "end_time": 187990.0,
      "text": "and update Siri throughout the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 187990.0,
      "end_time": 189900.0,
      "text": "as soon as the updates are ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 189900.0,
      "end_time": 192750.0,
      "text": "The bottom line: Siri has a long road ahead of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 192750.0,
      "end_time": 195420.0,
      "text": "and Amazon and Google aren't going to quit."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 195420.0,
      "end_time": 198429.0,
      "text": "But there are a lotta simple things Apple could do right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 198430.0,
      "end_time": 201000.0,
      "text": "that'd make the experience a whole lot better."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 201000.0,
      "end_time": 203910.0,
      "text": "It's not too late, but Apple needs to act fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 203910.0,
      "end_time": 205920.0,
      "text": "Here are shows available on iTunes."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 205920.0,
      "end_time": 209899.0,
      "text": "Vanderpump Rules, The Last Ship, Turn, Washing--"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 209900.0,
      "end_time": 210733.0,
      "text": "Shut up."
    }
  ]
}